title: #224: Take Me Out To The Ball Game (@PaulMorrissey)
itunes:title: Take Me Out To The Ball Game with Paul Morrissey
description: Paul Morrissey and I went to a Yankee game to talk about baseball. We got seats right behind the visitor's bullpen and we did a podcast from right there. We started on the walk to the subway, continued on the train a little, got lost some, got inside, met some Jews, had a dog, met some more people, and watched some more baseball. It was a great day.
